Big shoutout to: @theonlymc @oliviacaridi @zwyatt @lcshlmn @k_donnelly.23 @its_kirsti @leave_it_to_beavers for the prep and tear down! It couldn’t have happened without you! 

Never forget! The Monkey loves you ♥️

Photo dump (2/2)

WOW. WHAT AN AMAZING PARTY!!!! Huge thanks to all the people who made this happen, especially @jacobtolliver and @seangowdy who told me when I was driving home for family time that they would make it happen. It wouldn’t have happened without them. And to all the musicians, vendors, friends who helped and the nearly 300 guests who showed up - THANK YOU! You cheered up an old man when he needed it the most. I am fulfilled and I love you all. Thanks @isaacpittman for the reel!

To personally know this family is to love this family! ♥️ 
@jimmylswaggart @donnielswaggart @gabeswaggart and many of the other Swaggart family members have become friends of mine over the years. Dare I say “family”. 

On a very basic level - this makes my inner child giddy. It’s always special when you bond with your heroes. Jimmy Swaggart, along with Jerry Lee Lewis (and a few others), was a HUGE influence to my piano playing and style. As a kid, I would wake up early many a Sunday to watch Brother Swaggart lite that piano UP! It still blows my mind that 20 years later I had the opportunity to record with both Jimmy and Jerry Lee on the same record. 🤯

To the whole family:  I so appreciate you always taking me in, hosting me and being so welcoming.

Each time, I walk away so impressed at how genuine, real and human the connection is. 
Often times, in the secular world, you hear preconceived opinions surrounding televised ministries. Those opinions may be correct at times. They may be correct a lot of the time. But not here! The amount of good that this family does for the world (both Christian and temporal) is unfathomable. From 5am to the late hours of each night, this family is working around the clock to do good in the world. And that they do! 

I applaud your devotion, strength and determination. The same applies to each and every staff member. It’s jaw dropping. 

Forever a friend and ally, 

JT

I’m really looking forward to another night honoring this country icon! See you Wednesday, Texas!!! @therandytravis

When I’m not indulged in music, you’ll often find me outdoors. 
Landscaping, hardscaping and renovation projects are a true passion of mine. These things have always been an artistic recharge for me🔋 

For over a year now I have worn @bruntworkwear boots when working around my property in Ohio. They are hands down THE BEST boots I have ever worked in. 

I’m currently building a chapel, a stone wall/driveway entrance, a stone arch bridge, and more….all while simultaneously renovating my grandmother’s century old house. These boots have seen me through all of it! (And have saved my feet from a few nails along the way lol). 
A year later they’re still like new! 

If you need a great, comfortable pair of work boots, look no further!
